-- GROUP BY c.id, c.title, c.cwd;

-- ============================================================================
-- NOTES
-- ============================================================================

-- 1. RLS Policies: Existing RLS policies on messages table will automatically
--    apply to rows with ex_agent role since they filter by owner_id

-- 2. Triggers: Existing triggers (search vector update, conversation touch)
--    will automatically work with ex_agent messages

-- 3. Backward Compatibility: All changes use IF NOT EXISTS to allow safe
--    re-running of migration. Existing messages are unaffected (NULL values)

-- 4. Session ID Format: No constraints on ex_agent_session_id format.
--    Claude Code SDK uses UUID-like session identifiers

-- 5. Performance: Partial indexes minimize overhead for non-agent messages
--    while optimizing queries for agent messages

-- ============================================================================
-- END OF MIGRATION
-- ============================================================================
